  <a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/32803764/scale-the-entire-body-when-resizing-the-window">Stack Overflow answer</a><br/>
  <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en/docs/Mozilla/Mobile/Viewport_meta_tag">Mozilla's Docs</a><br/>

  <p>I added this tiny bit of code ...</p>

